tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE travel_expenses (
  receipt_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  category VARCHAR(50),
  amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE receipts (
  receipt_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  amount DECIMAL,
  receipt_date DATE,
  category VARCHAR,
  vendor VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE invoices (
  invoice_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  total_amount DECIMAL,
  issue_date DATE,
  due_date DATE,
  vendor VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE expenses (
  expense_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  amount DECIMAL,
  expense_date DATE,
  category VARCHAR,
  description TEXT,
  receipt_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE travel_plans (
  plan_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  traveler_id INT,
  destination VARCHAR,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);
